  + Lo lang: phan css hoc chua ky

psd => photoshop document

+ Trong thuc te: photoshop, figma, corel, indesign
+ Su dung duoc photoshop co ban:

+ mo file: ctrl + o
+ zoom: ctrl + (+/-)
+ Di chuyen: giu phim cach, cam va keo chuot
+ chot phai vao thanh thuoc: chon pixcel
+ tab
+ duong guide: duong chi dan
  + ctrl + ;
+ Layer: lop
+ gradient: chuyen mau

+ Lay hinh anh:
